-- ICBC Wins Argentine Approval for Standard Bank Deal, Xinhua Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-11-10T14:46:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-10/icbc-wins-argentine-approval-for-standard-bank-deal-xinhua-says.html
Industrial & Commercial Bank of
China Ltd.  received the Argentine central bank’s approval for
its purchase of an 80 percent stake in Standard Bank Group
Ltd.’s Argentine unit, Xinhua News Agency reported, citing the
Chinese lender.  That was the last approval needed for the acquisition,
Xinhua said today, citing an unidentified official with the
Beijing-based bank.  --Zhang Dingmin. Editors: Dylan Griffiths,  Chad Thomas .  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
Zhang Dingmin in Beijing at 
